txt.en:
The fell Haradrim Sorcerer Kang-kethek has come into the area. Defeat him before he turns the tide of the combat.

This quest starts with <rgb=#FFFF00>empty</rgb> Merit Rating.

<rgb=#00FF00>Merit Gain:</rgb>
* Defeat Kang-kethek
* Defeat Kang-kethek quickly
Defeat Kang-kethek quickly, before you and your allies succumb to his sorcery.
<rgb=#FF0000>You have left Kang-kethek unchallenged for too long.</rgb>
A fell Haradrim Sorcerer has come into the area. We must defeat him before he turns the tide against us.
